data.meta_description: WLW-AM 700 is a commercial news/talk radio station based in Cincinnati, Ohio, and owned by iHeart Media. A clear-channel, 50,000 watt, 24-hour station, WLW is branded as "Newsradio 700 WLW" and serves as the radio flagship of the Cincinnati Reds Radio Network and as a co-flagship station for the Cincinnati Bengals Radio Network.
